.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, grapefruit, grapes, lettuce, pomegranate, pumpkin
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, italian, pakistani, polish, russian, turkish
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating pomegranate and the russian##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the italian##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is in the middle##1
6. the polish is on the left of the australian##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
8. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the pakistani##1
9. the person eating grapes is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | lettuce | grapefruit | pomegranate | cauliflower | pumpkin | apple      | grapes  |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | turkish     | italian     | polish  | australian | chinese |

