.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, german, indian, mexican, pakistani, polish
7 different pets are kept: fish, goat, hamster, pony, rabbit, rat, turtle
 1. the mexican is on the left of the canadian##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the polish##1
 4. the german is on the left of the pakistani##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the indian is the owner of the pony##1
 7. the canadian is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the turtle and the indian##2
 9. the canadian is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the dutch is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | polish | mexican | canadian | dutch   | indian | german | pakistani |
| Pet           | rabbit | rat     | goat     | hamster | pony   | fish   | turtle    |

