.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, sprite, tea, water
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, malaysian, mexican, nigerian, pakistani, polish
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the nigerian##1
 3. the pakistani is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the mexican is between the person drinking juice and the pakistani##2
 7. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 8. the mexican is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is the chinese##1
10. the australian is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | juice    | sprite  | lemonade  | fanta  | water      | tea       | iced-tea |
| Nationality   | nigerian | mexican | pakistani | polish | australian | malaysian | chinese  |

