.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, disco, folk, house, metal, punk, rock
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, motorbike, ship, skateboard, train, van
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the fan of disco##1
3. the person driving the bike is between the fan of rock and the fan of classical##2
4. the fan of punk is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is the fan of house##1
9. the fan of metal is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | house      | metal | classical | folk | rock      | disco      | punk |
| Transport     | helicopter | train | van       | bike | motorbike | skateboard | ship |

