.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, paramedic, pilot, project-manager, scientist, videographer, writer
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, climbing, cycling, lacrosse, parkour, rowing, snowboarding
1. the pilot is on the left of the writer##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the scientist##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the videographer is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is parkour and the firefighter##2
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
8. the videographer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | scientist | firefighter | project-manager | videographer | paramedic | pilot     | writer |
| Sport   | cycling   | lacrosse    | snowboarding    | parkour      | climbing  | badminton | rowing |

