.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, milk
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, parkour, rowing, rugby, surfing, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person drinking iced-tea##2
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | coffee | cola    | hot-chocolate | fanta   | lemonade | milk    | iced-tea |
| Sport      | rowing | cricket | volleyball    | cycling | rugby    | parkour | surfing  |

