.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, adventure, disaster, horror, romance, satire, thriller
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, skateboard, taxi, tram, trike
1. the person watching action movies is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching romance movies is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person driving the bus is in the middle##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror     | satire | romance | disaster | thriller  | action |
| Transport     | quad-bike | skateboard | taxi   | bus     | trike    | motorbike | tram   |

