.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola, fanta, milk, mirinda, tea
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, gardening, hiking, magic-tricks, photography, singing
1. the person who's hobby is photography is the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is photography##2
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | coffee  | 7up       | tea         | milk         | fanta   | cola        | mirinda |
| Hobby      | singing | gardening | board-games | magic-tricks | cooking | photography | hiking  |

