4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
7. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | woodworking | singing       | puzzles    | rock-climbing | reading | hiking     | cooking       |
| Sport   | lacrosse    | skateboarding | volleyball | tennis        | sailing | ice-hockey | weightlifting |

