.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: documentary, epic, horror, musical, spy, western, zombie
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, folk, house, pop, punk, reggae, salsa
 1. the person watching documentary movies is the fan of salsa##1
 2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 3. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching musical movies and the fan of disco##2
 4. the person watching western movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching spy movies##2
 5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of house##1
 6. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is the fan of punk##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
10. the fan of pop is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | documentary | epic  | spy   | western | zombie | horror |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | salsa       | disco | house | reggae  | folk   | punk   |

